        <item>
            <title>【CES2025】MSI Raider 18 HX AI 亮相，搭載 RTX 5090 高性能手提電腦進入 AI 大時代</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/msi-raider-18-hx-ai/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=msi-raider-18-hx-ai</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/msi-raider-18-hx-ai/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 11:35:43 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MSI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Raider 18 HX AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[RTX 5090]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285875</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>MSI 在 CES 2025 發表全新手提電腦 Raider 18 HX AI，搭載 Nvidia RTX 5090 GPU 現時最火熱的高階圖像處理器，再加上 Intel Core Ultra 285HX 處理器，硬件性能達到全新極限。18 吋 Mini-LED 顯示屏具備 UHD+ 解像度、120Hz 更新率及 VESA DisplayHDR 1000 認證，無論是遊戲還是創意工作均表現出色。電腦還內置有 AI 功能，特別是 AI Robot 助理與 AI Noise Cancellation Pro 技術，進一步提升用戶體驗。今次我們記者 Edward 就到現場為大家直擊這部新機。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285908" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/msiaipoweredlaptop-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/msiaipoweredlaptop-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/msiaipoweredlaptop.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285909" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/msi_nb_raider18_a14v-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/msi_nb_raider18_a14v-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/msi_nb_raider18_a14v-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/msi_nb_raider18_a14v.jpg 700w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2>極致高性能 + 極致顯示技術</h2><p>Raider 18 HX AI 配備 18 吋 Mini-LED 顯示屏，解像度達到 UHD+（3840×2400 像素），並支援 120Hz 更新率和 VESA DisplayHDR 1000 認證。提供流暢畫面表現，更達到 100% 接近 DCI-P3 色域覆蓋，令暗部細節和色彩表現極致出眾。不論是進行高需求遊戲還是影像製作，都可提供專業級視覺體驗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1285876 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h32-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h32-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h32-scaled.jpg 506w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p>電腦內置流動版 Nvidia RTX 5090 GPU 配備 24GB GDDR7 記憶體，支援實時光線追蹤和 DLSS 技術，能應對最新遊戲的高畫質需求。同時其強大硬件設計更滿足專業影像處理與建模需求，為創作者和玩家帶來強效支援。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285906" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010865412-662x580.jpg" alt="" width="662" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010865412-662x580.jpg 662w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010865412.jpg 1027w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 662px" /></p><h2>AI 技術助力效率提升</h2><p>Raider 18 HX AI 配備了 AI Robot 助理，採用小型語言模型技術，支持文字指令操控，方便用戶快速完成應用程式啟動或系統設定修改。AI Noise Cancellation Pro 則能有效消除背景噪音，特別適用於線上會議或遊戲直播等需要高音質環境的場合。這些 AI 功能令使用者操作更加直觀高效，同時提高生產力和便利性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285905" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010865418-651x580.jpg" alt="" width="651" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010865418-651x580.jpg 651w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010865418.jpg 1011w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 651px" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
