            <title>【CES2025】MSI Claw 8 AI+ A2VM 手提遊戲電腦，全面搭載 Intel Core Ultra 7 258V 處理器</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/msi-claw-8-ai/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=msi-claw-8-ai</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/msi-claw-8-ai/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 10:22:40 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Claw 8 AI+]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MSI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提遊戲電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[攜帶式遊戲電腦]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285859</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在今年 CES 2025 消費科技展上，MSI 展出最新型號手提遊戲電腦 MSI Claw 8 AI+ A2VM、Claw 7 AI+ A2VM，兩部新機以升級處理器登場。兩款新機均搭載 Intel Core Ultra 7 258V 處理器，結合全新 Cooler Boost HyperFlow 雙風扇雙熱管散熱系統，確保在高負荷運行下仍能穩定表現，為遊戲玩家帶來全新的使用體驗。我們記者 Edward 就帶大家到會場睇睇真機。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285869" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-2-694x528.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="528" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-2-694x528.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-2.jpg 1184w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285863" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-583x580.jpg" alt="" width="583" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-583x580.jpg 583w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10.jpg 904w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 583px" /></p><h2>Claw 8 AI+ A2VM：結合高階性能與大螢幕</h2><p>Claw 8 AI+ A2VM 配備 8 吋 1920 x 1200 解像度觸控螢幕，支援 120Hz 更新率，帶來流暢視覺享受。機身搭載 32GB LPDDR5x 記憶體與 1TB NVMe M.2 SSD 儲存裝置，滿足大型遊戲運行需求。同時支援最新 Wi-Fi 7 和 Bluetooth 5.4 技術，提供高速穩定的網絡連接。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285864" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-1-610x580.jpg" alt="" width="610" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-1-610x580.jpg 610w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-1.jpg 947w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 610px" /></p><p>該機重量僅 765g，電池容量達 80Wh，為玩家提供長時間的續航能力。介面包括 2 個 Thunderbolt 4 埠、microSD 卡插槽與音訊插孔。MSI 更內建 Windows 11 Home 作業系統及 App Player，支援運行 Android 遊戲，進一步擴展遊戲選擇。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285867" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-3-458x580.jpg" alt="" width="458" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-3-458x580.jpg 458w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h10-3-scaled.jpg 710w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 458px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285868" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-1-472x580.jpg" alt="" width="472" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-1-472x580.jpg 472w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-1-scaled.jpg 733w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 472px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285870" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-3-520x580.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-3-520x580.jpg 520w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/vlcsnap2025010818h11-3.jpg 807w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 520px" /></p><h2>Claw 7 AI+ A2VM：輕巧與性能的完美平衡</h2><p>Claw 7 AI+ A2VM 作為 Claw A1M 的後繼機款，擁有 7 吋 1920 x 1080 解像度觸控螢幕，亦支援 120Hz 更新率，適合注重便攜性的用戶。內建與 Claw 8 相同的 32GB LPDDR5x 記憶體與 1TB NVMe M.2 SSD，提供一致的高速性能表現。</p><p>這款型號重量更輕，僅 675g，搭載 54.5Wh 電池，支援 Wi-Fi 6E 和 Bluetooth 5.3，適合外出攜帶使用。介面同樣包括 2 個 Thunderbolt 4 埠、microSD 卡插槽與音訊插孔，並預載 Windows 11 Home 系統及 App Player，讓用戶可靈活切換 Windows 和 Android 遊戲環境。</p><p>資料來源：MSI, Unwire.hk</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
